---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const today = new Date();
const formattedDate = `${today.toLocaleString('en-US', { month: 'long' })} ${today.getDate()}, ${today.getFullYear()}`;
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy | RecycleOldTech.com"
  description="Learn how RecycleOldTech.com collects, uses, and protects your information when you visit our website."
>
  <div class="bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="prose lg:prose-xl mx-auto">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        
        <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> {formattedDate}</p>
        
        <p>At <strong>RecycleOldTech.com</strong>, your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit our website.</p>
        
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        
        <p>We may collect certain non-personally identifiable information about your visit, including:</p>
        
        <ul>
          <li>IP address</li>
          <li>Browser type and version</li>
          <li>Pages visited and time spent on site</li>
          <li>Referring website or source</li>
          <li>Location data (at the city/region level)</li>
          <li>Device type and operating system</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>We do <strong>not</strong> collect any personally identifiable information unless you choose to provide it via a form submission (e.g., location search or contact form).</p>
        
        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        
        <p>We use the collected information to:</p>
        
        <ul>
          <li>Improve the performance and functionality of our website</li>
          <li>Understand user behavior and traffic patterns</li>
          <li>Help connect users with certified electronics recycling centers</li>
          <li>Monitor and analyze the effectiveness of our content and tools</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>3. Analytics and Tracking</h2>
        
        <p>RecycleOldTech.com uses the following third-party tools:</p>
        
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> and/or <strong>Vercel Analytics</strong> to monitor website traffic and usage</li>
          <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong> to serve ads that may be relevant to your interests</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>These tools may set cookies or collect usage data to help us better understand our visitors. You can disable cookies in your browser settings at any time.</p>
        
        <h2>4. Google AdSense and Cookies</h2>
        
        <p>We use <strong>Google AdSense</strong> to display advertisements. Google may use cookies or device identifiers to personalize ads and track performance.</p>
        
        <p>You can learn more about how Google uses data here:<br />
        <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads</a></p>
        
        <h2>5. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
        
        <p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>
        
        <ul>
          <li>Request access to your personal data</li>
          <li>Request deletion or correction of your data</li>
          <li>Opt out of data collection (via browser tools or ad opt-out links)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>To make such a request, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.</p>
        
        <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
        
        <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your information. However, please note that no online transmission or storage system is 100% secure.</p>
        
        <h2>7. Third-Party Links</h2>
        
        <p>RecycleOldTech.com may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of those sites.</p>
        
        <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with a new effective date.</p>
        
        <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
        
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, feel free to reach out through our:</p>
        
        <p><strong><a href="/contact">Contact Page</a></strong></p>
        
        <hr />
        
        <p><strong>Thank you for visiting RecycleOldTech.com and for doing your part to support responsible e-waste recycling.</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout> 
